        <li><span class="numbered-list__num">3</span><span class="numbered-list__text">用 <code>create_reflection_draft</code> 建立新的草稿</span></li>
        <li><span class="numbered-list__num">4</span><span class="numbered-list__text">用 <code>course://reflection-rules</code> 提供固定的反思規則</span></li>
        <li><span class="numbered-list__num">5</span><span class="numbered-list__text">用 <code>draft_reflection</code> 提供固定的反思工作流程</span></li>
